@startuml
title Simple Experiment Sequence

actor User
participant Pipeline
participant Simulator
participant CausalDiscovery
participant TIG
participant Partitioner
participant Evaluator

User -> Pipeline: Start experiment with config
Pipeline -> Simulator: Collect dataset
Simulator --> Pipeline: Dataset CSV

Pipeline -> CausalDiscovery: Build causal graph from dataset
CausalDiscovery --> Pipeline: Causal graph

Pipeline -> TIG: Compute task interaction graph
TIG --> Pipeline: Weighted TIG

Pipeline -> Partitioner: Partition TIG into communities
Partitioner --> Pipeline: Communities

Pipeline -> Evaluator: Configure and run evaluation
Evaluator --> User: Evaluation metrics

@enduml
